    &lt;xsl:template match=&quot;RunObject[@class=&#39;Entity&#39;]&quot;&gt;
        &lt;xsl:element name=&quot;Item&quot;&gt;
          &lt;xsl:apply-templates /&gt;
        &lt;/xsl:element&gt;
      &lt;/xsl:template&gt;

does not match anything:

 1. `RunObject` is in a namespace, and you are not using a prefix;
 2. XML is case-sensitive; the `class` attribute contains `&quot;entity&quot;`, not `&quot;Entity&quot;`.

It should work if you do:

    &lt;xsl:template match=&quot;s:RunObject[@class=&#39;entity&#39;]&quot;&gt;
        &lt;xsl:element name=&quot;Item&quot;&gt;
